{
  "stem": "18575.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 424.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Right When we got to Majdanek, they-- on a run, they opened the-- the cars, and there were people dead already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And on a run-- again, screaming and beating-- they run us to barracks in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And we had to undress naked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And there was a whole line of prisons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "There were a few thousands of the prisoners in the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Inside the barrack was a bench.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "There were several prisoner barbers sitting at the bench.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And naked, you had to pass them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "They would, with clippers, shave or clip your hair and your pubic hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And then you go further, and there was an SS officer standing, looking at you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And with a whip, he would direct you to the left or to the right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "There were two doors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And of course, later found out that one door was gas chamber, and one door was to the-- to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got in front of the barber, he asked me, what do you got here?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had my hand and foot in a-- in a-- in the rag, wrapped around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I opened up and showed him it was old, stinking pus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, stay with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't move.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while other prisoners kept going, I stayed with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The officer finally left the post, went outside to see how many-- possibly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what's his mind-- but walk outside to look how many prisoners are still there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the barber told me, go through the right door, or run to the right door.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to the right door, which was the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he saved my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know who he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never met him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
